{
  "id": "RAW_7f5fdb64",
  "title": "【第 3670 期】AI 工程实战：Claude Code 团队总结的六条反直觉缓存法则",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651278747&idx=1&sn=123edfcd2136f85e486428c863008faf",
  "date": "2026-03-16 01:02:00",
  "author": "前端早读课",
  "siteName": "前端早读课",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a387eeda&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FyuwWKyW2JczBacusG9Ww64tqCrFJrgicyh6hibOibkxszBqgLhiboibLaNNz6546MxQsaia26IrXC9FEhyTHz7neViadJgtn64s1f2WSnJYzIs7K80%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px !important;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">前言</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code 团队将提示缓存视为智能体架构的基石。本文系统梳理了他们在大规模优化缓存过程中总结的实战经验：从提示结构的精心编排、工具与模型的稳定性维护，到规划模式的巧妙设计与上下文压缩的缓存安全策略，揭示了一系列反直觉却至关重要的工程法则。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">今日前端早读课文章由&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code 团队</span><span leaf=\"\">@Thariq 分享，@飘飘编译。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">译文从这开始～～</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在工程领域，有句老话：\"缓存主宰一切\"，这条铁律同样适用于智能体。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">像 Claude Code 这样的长时运行智能体产品之所以可行，全靠提示缓存 —— 它能复用前序交互中的计算结果，从而大幅降低延迟和成本。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">提示缓存究竟是什么？它的工作原理是怎样的？技术上又该如何实现？欢迎阅读 @RLanceMartin 关于提示缓存及我们最新自动缓存功能的详细文章。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">提示缓存：<a href=\"https://x.com/RLanceMartin/status/2024573404888911886\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/RLanceMartin/status/2024573404888911886</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Claude Code 中，我们的整个架构都围绕提示缓存而建。高缓存命中率不仅能降低成本，还能帮助我们为订阅用户提供更宽裕的速率限制。因此，我们对缓存命中率设置了实时告警，一旦命中率过低，便会立即启动事故响应。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651278239&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=713d01d28d51c2f060ac516ddd8556f8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3631期】No-Vary-Search：用一个新 HTTP 头拯救你的缓存性能！\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3631期】No-Vary-Search：用一个新 HTTP 头拯救你的缓存性能！</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">以下是我们在大规模优化提示缓存过程中总结出的经验 —— 其中不少颇为反直觉。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">1、为缓存精心编排提示结构</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5514705882352942\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"680\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503795091\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22fc5526&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FyuwWKyW2JczlOt0jvFrosqHBNibyfFkQ8nTfFGibaV6JDn4cSoRTuzBKWoe67wdHcXhnAB7g9NjsjL5OfjtQWwbicANWvicdyocCdGtK9PLq0oE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">提示缓存基于前缀匹配机制 ——API 会从请求的起始位置开始缓存，一直到每个&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">cache_control</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;断点为止。这意味着内容的排列顺序至关重要：你需要让尽可能多的请求共享同一前缀。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">最佳实践是：静态内容在前，动态内容在后。在 Claude Code 中，具体布局如下：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;padding-left:2em;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">静态系统提示 &amp; 工具定义（全局缓存）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">Claude.MD 文件（项目级缓存）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">会话上下文（会话级缓存）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0.25em;list-style-type: disc;\">\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">对话消息</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样就能最大化不同会话之间的缓存命中率。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这套结构可能出乎意料地脆弱！我们曾多次打破这个排列顺序，原因包括：在静态系统提示中加入了精确的时间戳、工具定义的顺序被非确定性地打乱、更新了工具参数（例如 AgentTool 可以调用哪些子智能体）等等。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651277436&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c42d1bb443644528beae154177405565&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【第3589期】写好工具，智能体才更聪明：Claude 的自我优化实践\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【第3589期】写好工具，智能体才更聪明：Claude 的自我优化实践</a></span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">2、用消息传递更新信息</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">有时提示中的信息会过时，例如时间变化或用户修改了文件。你可能会想直接更新提示内容，但这会导致缓存失效，最终可能让用户付出高昂的代价。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">不妨换个思路：将更新信息通过下一轮对话的消息传入。在 Claude Code 中，我们会在下一条用户消息或工具返回结果中添加一个&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&lt;system-reminder&gt;</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;标签，附上更新后的信息（例如 \"现在是星期三\"），从而保住缓存。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">3、不要在会话中途切换模型</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">提示缓存是按模型隔离的，这使得缓存的成本计算变得颇为反直觉。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">假设你已经和 Opus 对话了 10 万个 token，此时想问一个比较简单的问题。切换到 Haiku 反而比让 Opus 直接回答更贵，因为你需要为 Haiku 从头构建提示缓存。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651273075&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=54acca473c3e1f8df8990f32880b7631&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【早阅】会话令牌和JWT结合的优势\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【早阅】会话令牌和JWT结合的优势</a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果确实需要切换模型，最好的方式是使用子智能体：由 Opus 准备一段 \"交接\" 消息，将任务移交给另一个模型处理。在 Claude Code 中，我们经常这样做 —— 使用 Haiku 驱动的 Explore 探索智能体就是典型例子。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">4、绝不在会话中途增删工具</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在对话过程中更改工具集，是人们最常犯的破坏缓存的错误之一。这看起来很合理 —— 只给模型提供当前需要的工具嘛。但由于工具定义是缓存前缀的一部分，增加或移除任何一个工具都会导致整段对话的缓存全部失效。</span></p>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">规划模式 —— 围绕缓存进行设计</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">规划模式是围绕缓存约束进行功能设计的绝佳范例。直觉上的做法是：当用户进入规划模式时，将工具集替换为只读工具。但这会破坏缓存。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们的做法是：始终保留全部工具，把&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">EnterPlanMode</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ExitPlanMode</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;本身也设计为工具。当用户切换到规划模式时，智能体会收到一条系统消息，说明当前处于规划模式并给出相应指令 —— 浏览代码库、不要编辑文件、计划完成后调用&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ExitPlanMode</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。工具定义自始至终不变。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这还带来了一个额外好处：既然&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">EnterPlanMode</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;本身就是模型可以调用的工具，模型在遇到棘手问题时，能够自主进入规划模式，而不会造成任何缓存中断。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">5、工具搜索 —— 延迟加载而非移除</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">同样的原则也适用于我们的工具搜索功能。Claude Code 可能加载了数十个 MCP 工具，将它们全部塞进每次请求的成本很高，但在对话中途移除又会破坏缓存。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们的解决方案是：延迟加载（defer_loading）。我们不移除工具，而是发送轻量级的占位符 —— 仅包含工具名称，并标记&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">defer_loading: true</span></code><span leaf=\"\">—— 模型在需要时可以通过&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace;font-size: 13.6px;padding: 0.2em 0px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);border-radius: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ToolSearch</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;工具去 \"发现\" 它们。完整的工具定义只有在模型选中时才会加载。这样，缓存前缀始终保持稳定：相同的占位符始终以相同的顺序存在。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">好消息是，你可以通过我们的 API 直接使用工具搜索功能来简化这一过程。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">6、上下文分叉 —— 压缩</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5088235294117647\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"680\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-style: none;display: block;margin: 0px auto 16px;max-width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"503795089\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f7e2994&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FyuwWKyW2Jcx4k6qGyjRibL19pCCZWPicic6iaoFiaalcJ5fhSkAFEHfEodUBaYIfFWCMO4BpjWxmHjmr9cOIncFNpX59Q3CMEGC11iaRN4wSQPMM8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">当上下文窗口用尽时，就需要进行压缩（Compaction）。我们会对当前对话进行摘要，然后以这份摘要开启一个新的会话继续对话。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">出人意料的是，压缩在提示缓存方面有许多反直觉的边界情况。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">特别是在执行压缩时，我们需要将整段对话发送给模型以生成摘要。如果这是一个使用不同系统提示且不包含工具的独立 API 调用（也就是最简单的实现方式），那么它与主对话的缓存前缀完全不匹配。你将为所有输入 token 支付全价，极大地增加用户的成本。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&amp;mid=2651274301&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=cd81adafd6f785471d0ee5ae4d54012c&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【早阅】如何有效清除NPM和NPX缓存？\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【早阅】如何有效清除NPM和NPX缓存？</a></span></p>\n  <h5 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">解决方案 —— 缓存安全的分叉</span></h5>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在执行压缩时，我们使用与父会话完全相同的系统提示、用户上下文、系统上下文和工具定义。我们将父会话的对话消息放在前面，然后将压缩指令作为一条新的用户消息追加在末尾。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">从 API 的视角来看，这个请求与父会话的最后一次请求几乎一模一样 —— 相同的前缀、相同的工具、相同的历史记录 —— 因此缓存前缀得以复用。唯一的新增 token 仅仅是压缩指令本身。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，这也意味着我们需要预留一个 \"压缩缓冲区\"，确保上下文窗口中有足够的空间容纳压缩消息和摘要的输出 token。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">压缩的实现颇为棘手，但好在你不必亲自踩这些坑 —— 基于我们在 Claude Code 中积累的经验，我们已经将压缩功能直接内置到了 API 中，你可以在自己的应用中直接使用这些模式。</span></p>\n  <h4 data-edit=\"早编辑器\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:18px;line-height:1.25;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:24px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">经验总结</span></h4>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">1、提示缓存是前缀匹配。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">前缀中任何位置的改动都会使其之后的所有缓存失效。你的整个系统架构都应围绕这一约束来设计。把顺序排对，大部分缓存效果自然水到渠成。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">2、用消息代替系统提示的修改。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">你可能想通过编辑系统提示来实现进入规划模式、更新日期等功能，但实际上，将这些信息插入对话消息中是更好的选择。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">3、不要在对话中途切换工具或模型。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">用工具来建模状态转换（如规划模式），而不是更改工具集。用延迟加载代替移除工具。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">4、像监控服务可用性一样监控缓存命中率。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们对缓存失效设置了告警，并将其视为线上事故处理。哪怕只有几个百分点的缓存未命中率，也会对成本和延迟产生巨大影响。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">5、分叉操作必须共享父会话的前缀。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你需要执行附属计算（压缩、摘要、技能执行），请使用相同的缓存安全参数，以确保能命中父会话前缀的缓存。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code 从第一天起就围绕提示缓存而建，如果你正在构建智能体，也应如此。</span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_common_product_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-product data-windowproduct=\"v1=HF-eQic78oOmKgqQA1vNRcWfSSqWS5oYJ7eU9NOvtX93B90fX9kfSxsox70funDMqN9kUJaXi1qF7g\" data-cardtype=\"1\" data-title=\"卓越管理者的“瑞士军刀”\" data-type=\"0\"></mp-common-product></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;margin-bottom:0px !important;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">关于本文</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">译者：@飘飘</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">作者：@Thariq</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">原文：<a href=\"https://x.com/trq212/status/2024574133011673516\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/trq212/status/2024574133011673516</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章系统总结 Claude Code 团队在提示缓存上的工程实践，强调缓存不是性能细节，而是智能体架构的一等约束。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章系统总结 Claude Code 团队在提示缓存上的工程实践，强调缓存不是性能细节，而是智能体架构的一等约束。",
  "summary": "本文围绕提示缓存给出了一组高价值、反直觉的智能体工程法则：提示前缀编排、消息替代系统提示更新、会话中不切模型/不变更工具集、规划模式工具化、工具延迟加载、以及上下文压缩时的缓存安全分叉。其最大价值在于把「缓存命中率」从成本优化指标提升为系统可靠性指标，并结合真实故障模式解释为什么某些看似合理的实现会导致大面积缓存失效。文章方法具体、可操作、迁移性强，适合构建长会话 Agent 的团队直接落地。作为经验总结类内容，理论抽象不算多，但工程含金量很高。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "提示缓存应被视为系统架构约束，而非后置优化项。",
      "explanation": "由于缓存基于前缀匹配，前缀任意位置变化都会引发级联失效，要求从设计阶段就稳定系统提示、工具定义和上下文结构。"
    },
    {
      "point": "状态切换应通过消息与工具建模，而不是修改核心前缀。",
      "explanation": "规划模式、信息更新、工具搜索等能力通过消息层或占位机制实现，可在不破坏缓存前缀的前提下完成动态行为。"
    },
    {
      "point": "上下文压缩与分叉请求必须复用父会话前缀。",
      "explanation": "压缩若采用独立调用路径会导致全量 token 重新计费；使用缓存安全参数分叉可显著降低成本并维持响应稳定性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "缓存主宰一切，这条铁律同样适用于智能体。",
    "不要在对话中途切换工具或模型。",
    "像监控服务可用性一样监控缓存命中率。"
  ],
